Nobanion is a Faer√ªnian demigod of the Forgotten Realms campaign setting. He is the deity of royalty, lions and feline beasts and also good beasts.
Nobanion's Realm in the Beastlands, in the daylit Layer Krigala, is called the Pridelands. It is a vast savanna dotted with groves of trees. His petitioners take the form of lions or wemics. 

